-- Isaac Grows Into Hurricane Southeast of Louisiana, NHC Says
-- B y   C h a r l o t t e   P o r t e r
-- 2012-08-28T16:28:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-28/isaac-grows-into-hurricane-southeast-of-louisiana-nhc-says.html
Hurricane Isaac developed today 75
miles (121 kilometers) south-southeast of the mouth of the
Mississippi River, with top sustained winds of 75 mph, the
National Hurricane Center said in a special advisory.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
